'André Tanneberger', under the stage name of 'ATB', (born February 26, 1973 in
Freiberg, Saxony, Germany)<ref></ref> is a German DJ, musician, and producer of
trance music. According to the official world DJ rankings governed by [[DJ
Magazine]], ATB was ranked #11 in 2009.<ref></ref> as well as in 2010 and went
down to #15 in 2011.<ref></ref> In 2011, he was ranked as world number 1
according to "The DJ List".<ref></ref>
